    "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\n`:lsp` and `:log` don't use EXX error codes for their error messages.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nAdd them.\r\n\r\nRestructures the documentation for `:lsp` so it is formatted the same as files like `runtime/doc/editing.txt`.\r\n\r\nAlso removes the `--add-comments` flag from `xgettext` because it dumped a bunch of comments from lua files into the `.pot` files.",
